{"title":"卡梅尔的故事","date":"2020-01-13T14:41:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jan 13, 2020","L":"01/13/2020","MM-DD":"01-13"},"thumbnail":"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/18/LKB5StU1eXORz72.jpg","link":"2020/01/13/卡梅尔的故事","comments":true,"tags":["诗","陪伴"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-02-10T17:07:33.988Z","content":"<p>人群中的你<br>\n目不转睛的我<br>\n预支多年的光景<br>\n堵上未名的期盼<br>\n终于握住了你</p>\n<p>那是条坎坷曲折<br>\n但充满神秘而绮丽的小路<br>\n你向我轻语：<br>\n——握紧<br>\n我知道我依靠的是什么</p>\n<p>为你拂去落尘<br>\n一路陪伴的我的伙伴<br>\n每一个棱角我都曾触摸<br>\n你心中闪耀的每一片光羽<br>\n都在画框中温存</p>\n<p>时光如潮<br>\n不过让你的沧桑厉现风俊<br>\n无恐空盼，只许相随</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>故乡</em><br>\n<em>2020.01.13</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n","prev":{"title":"Promises第三章","link":"2020/01/17/PromisesChapter3"},"next":{"title":"Promises第二章","link":"2020/01/09/PromisesChapter2"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2020/01/13/卡梅尔的故事/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"白桦树下的人","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"February 11, 2020"}}